*For every new terminal opened, do underlay workspace sourcing.
**For every operation in overlay workspace, do overlay workspace sourcing.

Open turtlesim simulator using command below:

    ros2 run turtlesim turtlesim_node

To make the turtle run using keyboard
Open another terminal*
    ros2 run turtlesim turtle_teleop_key
Keep this terminal and turtlesim window side by side. Click on teleop terminal and use arrow keys to navigate turtle.

Try commands
    ros2 topic list
    ros2 node list

To make the turtle run using terminal command
Stop teleop terminal
Open another terminal*

    ros2 topic pub /turtle1/cmd_vel geometry_msgs/msg/Twist "{linear: {x: 2.0, y: 0.0, z: 0.0}, angular: {x: 0.0, y: 0.0, z: 0.0}}"

Stop terminals by Ctrl+C
